comments.body:
@kuguma I did some research on this, and I don't feel comfortable passing any safe flags through git. Based on my research, this is a flutter/git issue. https://github.com/flutter/flutter/issues/123995

As much as I like to make everything magical, solving this problem creates a possible security issue, even if it's a small vector, and FVm needs to assume that git can run fine on this.

I will however maybe make this a bit more prominent in the docs.
